"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2488203-governor-sindh-honours-olympic-gold-medallist-arshad-nadeem-with-rs20m-reward\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"EC  Kamran Tessori praised Arshad Nadeem's dedication and a grand reception was hosted for him at Governor House  Olympic gold medallist Arshad Nadeem was warmly welcomed by Governor Sindh Kamran Khan Tessori at the Governor House on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 2, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Commission\", \"score\": 0.9292619670664316, \"rank\": 0.06415960025771804, \"text\": \"EC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Commission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Commission\"}, {\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamran_Akmal\", \"score\": 0.9976497290704666, \"rank\": 0.00235580770996492, \"text\": \"Kamran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamran_Akmal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamran_Akmal\"}, {\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9477565636640708, \"rank\": 0.03671018120122133, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}, {\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sindh\", \"score\": 0.9999769155765209, \"rank\": 1.9495298010287538e-05, \"text\": \"Sindh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sindh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.