rachi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also expressed appreciation for the live coverage by the media, which allowed the entire nation to share in the celebrations.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten,                     redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is                     copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}]}"